nodes.text: BO-N1 was a service droid who worked at the droid spa on Coruscant during the Clone Wars.

BO-N1 was voiced by Angelique Perrin, who also voiced fellow spa droid SN-D1 in the eighth episode of the third season of Star Wars: The Clone Wars, "Evil Plans." Though not named in the episode itself, BO-N1's name is given in the episode's credits.
